OL,6,FWATCH: ITV News Meridian's Report is
OL,7,Fby Charlotte Wilkins
OL,9,FOnce known as the Palace by the Sea,
OL,10,FThe Grand Hotel in Brighton opened to
OL,11,Fgreat fanfare in 1864. Australian
OL,12,Fairmen lodged there during the Second
OL,13,FWorld War; Abba used the venue to
OL,14,Fcelebrate their after-party following
OL,15,Ftheir historic win at Eurovision in
OL,16,F1974 and who could forget the
OL,17,Fdevastating IRA Bomb of 1984.
