OL,3,CBrighton's Grand Hotel celebrates 160
OL,4,Cyears with 160 afternoon teas
OL,6,FIf walls could talk, the Grand Hotel
OL,7,Fin Brighton would certainly have a lot
OL,8,Fto say. It's still one of the city's
OL,9,Fmost iconic and go-to places, whether
OL,10,Fthat's to celebrate weddings,
OL,11,Fanniversaries or romantic getaways.
OL,13,FAnd over the last 160 years it's also
OL,14,Fbeen a place where people have enjoyed
OL,15,Fjust being together. To celebrate the
OL,16,Fhotel's special milestone 160
OL,17,Fafternoon teas have been served to
OL,18,Fhighlight the work of Brighton's
OL,19,FLoneliness Charity - Together Co.
OL,21,FCEO of Together Co, April Baker says
