OL,3,CBrighton's Grand Hotel celebrates 160
OL,4,Cyears with 160 afternoon teas
OL,6,F"We've been working in the city for
OL,7,Fover 20 years. Most importantly it's
OL,8,Fabout creating connections, to reduce
OL,9,Floneliness and isolation. We do that
OL,10,Fthrough befriending programmes where
OL,11,Fwe match up neighbours to flourish and
OL,12,Fhave friendships and we have social
OL,13,Fprescribing. We put on events like
OL,14,Fthis."
OL,16,FJean Chapman was introduced to
OL,17,Fbefriender Jackie Grier through
OL,18,FTogether Co just after the death of
OL,19,Fher husband.
